title: Unquote
alt: I guess it's a saying from the Old Country.
transcript:
[Two figures with spiky hair and backpacks are conversing. One is riding in a hover-car, or similar.]
Future Hair: Bye!
Friend: May the Force be with you!
Future Hair: Huh?
Friend: It's just something my grandma used to say. No idea what it means.[Caption below the panel:]
I wonder on what date Star Wars will be quoted for the last time.
